{"name":"Flip of Fate","type":"action","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger </strong>The target of your Exploit Vulnerability is the target of a check from you or a creature within 30 feet.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements </strong>You're holding your coin implement and are benefiting from Exploit Vulnerability.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You flip your coin, winding fate around it like a thread in your favor. Roll a @Check[type:flat|dc:11].</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The triggering check gains a +2 circumstance bonus, +3 if you are a master in Arcana, Nature, Occultism, or Religion. The bonus increases to +4 if you are legendary.</p>\n<p><strong>Success </strong>The triggering check gains a +1 circumstance bonus.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> Fate laughs, you impose a -1 circumstance penalty on the check, this result replaces the Flip of Fate's fortune trait with Misfortune.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.foundry-pf2e-thaumaturges-wrath.thaumaturges-wrath.DQ2sY3zompc43ULE]{Effect: Flip of Fate}</p>"},"source":{"value":"Thaumaturge's Wrath"},"traits":{"value":["divination","fortune","magical","manipulate","thaumaturge"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.791,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-09-30T01:17:19.196+01:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.286","system":"4.1.3"}}},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"43Qf3EpsW62vgBEI":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.c9Pc48DMSQneaOUU"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.1.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1664497039200,"modifiedTime":1664675233207,"lastModifiedBy":"43Qf3EpsW62vgBEI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"0CXbjw5Mkqh6vTIf"}
{"name":"Fateful Habit","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/features/feats/feats.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You're holding your coin implement</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You rub, spin, kiss, or otherwise address your coin attempting to call fate to your aid. Choose a specific type of check (except flat checks), such as an attack roll or an Acrobatics skill check. Until the start of your next turn, you may use @Compendium[foundry-pf2e-thaumaturges-wrath.thaumaturges-wrath.0CXbjw5Mkqh6vTIf]{Flip of Fate} with the following trigger: An ally within 30 feet attempts the type of check you chose with Fateful Habit.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Thaumaturge's Wrath"},"traits":{"value":["thaumaturge"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.793,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-10-02T01:10:43.284+01:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.286","system":"4.1.3"}}},"level":{"value":2},"featType":{"value":"class"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":1},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"coin implement"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"43Qf3EpsW62vgBEI":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.q1YbaZ1oiT4ID9M0"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.1.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1664669443288,"modifiedTime":1664679228541,"lastModifiedBy":"43Qf3EpsW62vgBEI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"0QLFjMQNqymsPeQ9"}
{"name":"Band","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/equipment/worn-items/other-worn-items/belt-of-the-five-kings.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Bands take many forms, from rings of precious metal, to cords of leather, sashes, or any other symbol of your bond to another person. You may strongly present a band worn on your hand as an Interact action without removing it, to do so the adorned hand must be free, and doing so counts as holding your band implement. Band implements are associated with the astrological signs of the newlyweds and the harrow cards of the marriage and the survivor.</p>\n<h3>Initiate Benefit</h3>\n<p>Your band allows you to bear the burden for your allies. You gain the @UUID[Compendium.foundry-pf2e-thaumaturges-wrath.thaumaturges-wrath.hsCxaKCNh3HOxovN]{Share Burden} reaction.</p>\n<h3>Adept Benefit</h3>\n<p>You can share the load of those conditions that would harm your allies. Share Burden \"adds or would gain a condition with a value\" to its trigger. Any triggering ally that would gain a condition with a value, such as sickened 2, reduces the condition value by 1 and you gain that condition with a value of 1 for the duration your ally would have suffered it. If the same effect causes both damage and a condition, you may choose to accept both effects or only one.</p>\n<h3>Intensify Vulnerability</h3>\n<p>The bonds you forge protect your allies at all times against the target of your @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.fodJ3zuwQsYnBbtk]{Exploit Vulnerability}. Allies in a 15-foot emanation gain a +1 status bonus to AC and saves against the target of your Exploit Vulnerability.</p>\n<h3>Paragon Benefit</h3>\n<p>When you use Share Burden, You may accept as much of the triggering damage as you would like, in any combination if multiple damage types are present. When a triggering ally would gain a condition, you may choose to gain that condition instead even if it does not have a value.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Thaumaturge's Wrath"},"traits":{"value":["thaumaturge"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[{"key":"GrantItem","uuid":"Compendium.foundry-pf2e-thaumaturges-wrath.thaumaturges-wrath.hsCxaKCNh3HOxovN"}],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.791,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-09-28T17:23:57.366+01:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.286","system":"4.1.3"}}},"level":{"value":1},"featType":{"value":"classfeature"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"43Qf3EpsW62vgBEI":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.iqCjvJGVj6pBtl2f"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.1.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1664382237370,"modifiedTime":1664675233237,"lastModifiedBy":"43Qf3EpsW62vgBEI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"1wWrUclKEZEzseF1"}
