{"name":"Stake Self","type":"action","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Frequency&nbsp;</strong>once per day</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You impale yourself with your own stake to absorb the massive amount of power stored within, but at the potential cost of your own life. For the next minute, you gain a +3 status bonus to attack rolls, damage rolls, and saving throws as well as a +30-foot status bonus to your Speed. Unfortunately, this power constantly overwhelms your body while the stake destroys your heart; you take [[/r {@actor.level}[persistent]]]@Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.lDVqvLKA6eF3Df60]{persistent damage equal to your level} that cannot end so long as you&rsquo;re benefiting from these bonuses. At the end of the duration, or by spending an action to pull out the stake, you end the benefits it grants and must attempt a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:40] save. On a success, you become @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.4D2KBtexWXa6oUMR]{Drained 1}, @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.4D2KBtexWXa6oUMR]{Drained 2} on a failure. On a critical failure, you become drained 2 and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.6uEgoh53GbXuHpTF]{Paralyzed} for 1 minute.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.foundry-pf2e-thaumaturges-wrath.thaumaturges-wrath.406O0sSnEyhlBKOh]{Effect: Stake Self}</p>"},"source":{"value":"Thaumaturge's Wrath"},"traits":{"value":["curse","transmutation"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.793,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-10-01T17:20:43.335+01:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.286","system":"4.1.3"}}},"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":1},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false,"frequency":{"max":1,"per":"day"}},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"43Qf3EpsW62vgBEI":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.hENdvolc0kR7DjSh"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.1.3","coreVersion":"10.286","createdTime":1664641243338,"modifiedTime":1664675233296,"lastModifiedBy":"43Qf3EpsW62vgBEI"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"5RnfgDQkWZkCAqHM"}
{"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/features/classes/implement-adept.webp","name":"Implement Adept","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>This thaumaturge class feature is for use with the Thaumaturge's Wrath content module. It includes automation to integrate the new implements into the thaumaturge class.</strong></p>\n<p>You have deepened your connection to one of your implements, unlocking its adept power. Choose one of your implements and gain the adept benefit for that implement.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Thaumaturge's Wrath"},"traits":{"value":["thaumaturge"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[{"adjustName":false,"choices":[{"label":"PF2E.SpecificRule.Thaumaturge.Implement.Amulet","predicate":["feature:amulet"],"value":"amulet"},{"label":"PF2E.SpecificRule.Thaumaturge.Implement.Bell","predicate":["feature:bell"],"value":"bell"},{"label":"PF2E.SpecificRule.Thaumaturge.Implement.Chalice","predicate":["feature:chalice"],"value":"chalice"},{"label":"PF2E.SpecificRule.Thaumaturge.Implement.Lantern","predicate":["feature:lantern"],"value":"lantern"},{"label":"PF2E.SpecificRule.Thaumaturge.Implement.Mirror","predicate":["feature:mirror"],"value":"mirror"},{"label":"PF2E.SpecificRule.Thaumaturge.Implement.Regalia","predicate":["feature:regalia"],"value":"regalia"},{"label":"PF2E.SpecificRule.Thaumaturge.Implement.Tome","predicate":["feature:tome"],"value":"tome"},{"label":"PF2E.SpecificRule.Thaumaturge.Implement.Wand","predicate":["feature:wand"],"value":"wand"},{"label":"PF2E.SpecificRule.Thaumaturge.Implement.Weapon","predicate":["feature:weapon"],"value":"weapon"},{"label":"Band","predicate":["feature:band"],"value":"band"},{"label":"Coffin","predicate":["feature:coffin"],"value":"coffin"},{"label":"Coin","predicate":["feature:coin"],"value":"coin"},{"label":"Mask","predicate":["feature:mask"],"value":"mask"},{"label":"Nail","predicate":["feature:nail"],"value":"nail"},{"label":"Ossuary","predicate":["feature:ossuary"],"value":"ossuary"},{"label":"Stake","predica